('12', '54', 'Margosita', 'margaret.lafleur@gmail.com', '', '76.21.35.243', '2009-06-14 20:49:00', '2009-06-15 00:49:00', 'I\'ve only just started reading your blog... so this comment is mostly to say hey, that I\'m reading, and that this post was great.\r\n\r\nHey.\r\nI\'m a reader.\r\nI enjoyed this post- and especially the Writer\'s Digest and Cosmo comparison.  Perfect!', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.4; en-US; rv:1.9.0.11) Gecko/2009060214 Firefox/3.0.11', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
