('16', '54', 'Laura Ellen Scott', 'lscott18@verizon.net', 'http://probablyjustastory.blogspot.com/', '96.241.122.234', '2009-06-16 08:29:03', '2009-06-16 12:29:03', 'excellent note about Writer\'s Digest, couldn\'t agree more. may steal that chunk. my students, and a surprising number of my colleagues, seem to equate ubiquity with authority.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.5; en-US; rv:1.9.0.11) Gecko/2009060214 Firefox/3.0.11', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
('18', '54', 'Rion', 'rion.amilcar.scott@gmail.com', 'http://datsunflambe.blogspot.com', '173.66.64.49', '2009-06-17 23:41:06', '2009-06-18 03:41:06', 'Denzel is one of my favorite dudes, but I see where you are coming from with the smugness. I think it\'s a new trait of his though. Something he\'s developed in the last 5 years or so. Maybe 7. Ever since people started sweating him.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_7; en-us) AppleWebKit/525.28.3 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/3.2.3 Safari/525.28.3', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
