('21', '54', 'Roxane', 'roxane@roxanegay.com', 'http://www.roxanegay.com', '71.13.217.52', '2009-06-19 20:32:55', '2009-06-20 00:32:55', 'Rion, the smugness is definitely new. I thought he was great in that one movie with John Lithgow, where he played a district attorney. Since he won the Oscsr though, I find him to be unbearable. Also, he cheats on Juanita like a dog. Be discrete, man!', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.5; en-US; rv:1.9.0.11) Gecko/2009060214 Firefox/3.0.11', '', '0', '1', 'N'),
