('93', '105', 'david erlewine', 'daveerlewine@yahoo.com', '', '68.33.40.219', '2009-06-27 23:03:19', '2009-06-28 03:03:19', '(nodding)\r\n\r\nWell put, Roxane, I can\'t argue with anything you say here.  Nicely stated!', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.0; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; MDDC; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30618)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
