('7086', '173', 'Lauren Becker', 'ljb921@gmail.com', 'http://www.lauren-graysheep.blogspot.com', '76.102.143.209', '2009-07-28 13:16:52', '2009-07-28 17:16:52', 'Great post!  You are the queen of rants, a position for which I was in the running.  May I be princess?  Maybe duchess?\r\n\r\nThanks for the many shout-outs on the summer issue of DOGZPLOT.  I was lucky to work with amazing contributors.  You know how it goes, woman who puts out both stellar web and print editions every single time!', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.0; Trident/4.0; GTB6; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; Media Center PC 5.0; .NET CLR 3.0.04506; yie8)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
