('14320', '203', 'Sara', 'saracrowley@btinternet.com', 'http://asalted.blogspot.com/', '86.144.36.236', '2009-08-11 04:31:08', '2009-08-11 08:31:08', 'Swish new look!\r\n\r\nAnd \"submission void\" is exactly the way to describe it. Hope you get responses soon. I subbed a story back in January to a place that said I\'d hear back by April. Nope. I now want to sub that presumably rejected piece to a competition that states it can\'t be in consideration anywhere else so I query emailed the first place. Still nothing. SIGH. I also sent a query email to a different magazine a few weeks back, again, no reply. It\'s so frustrating that stories get held up in this way. It must send you nuts, I know how promptly you send word to all who sub work to Pank.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_7; en-gb) AppleWebKit/530.19.2 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0.2 Safari/530.19', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
