('16841', '221', 'Ethel Rohan', 'ethelrohan@gmail.com', '', '24.4.57.196', '2009-08-18 12:54:32', '2009-08-18 16:54:32', 'Congratulations on \"Important Things To Know About Career Girls.\" I loved all the \"so that it is known ...\"\r\n\r\nSuccess is sweet and so much more besides, including maddening. Take an unabashed bow, we\'re all giving you a standing ovation.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US) AppleWebKit/530.5 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/2.0.172.39 Safari/530.5', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
('16843', '221', 'Cate', 'catiewaier@gmail.com', 'http://lifeaftermfa.wordpress.com', '128.2.38.119', '2009-08-18 15:46:01', '2009-08-18 19:46:01', 'I think you\'re right that the criticism of your own work never really stops. If someone says they like something of mine, my first thought is always along the lines of, \"but didn\'t they notice THIS, which is terrible...or THIS, which smacks of amateur garbage?!\" And so instead of feeling good about myself, I\'ve only succeeded in rehashing all my flaws, real and imagined. \r\n\r\nThough I hear the best writers are terribly insecure so maybe I\'m on the right track... ;)\r\n\r\nAt any rate: this is important to hear and to be thinking about, for all of us. Thank you.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.13) Gecko/2009073022 Firefox/3.0.13', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
