('30174', '268', 'Ethel Rohan', 'ethelrohan@gmail.com', '', '24.4.57.196', '2009-09-16 16:20:16', '2009-09-16 20:20:16', 'Congratulations, Roxane. The voice here is great. Wonderful restraint throughout that makes this all the more moving and real. \"We grow into our reputations\" really resonated.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US) AppleWebKit/530.5 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/2.0.172.43 Safari/530.5', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
