('30646', '366', 'KWDragon', 'kwdragon@pasty.net', '', '141.219.202.112', '2009-12-05 20:04:51', '2009-12-06 00:04:51', 'Your description of the academic job market is spot on, and I would expect nothing less.  If you ever need a non-academic icepack, like perhaps a latte or a tequila, let me know.  I will provide, and we shall commiserate.\r\n\r\nMan, job hunting truly sucks like a Hoover in a black hole.  Vacuum cleaner or president, take your pick.\r\n\r\nHang in there.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.5; en-US; rv:1.9.1.5) Gecko/20091102 Firefox/3.5.5', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
