('30653', '366', 'FC', 'fechong@mtu.edu', '', '71.13.211.87', '2009-12-06 19:54:26', '2009-12-06 23:54:26', 'Sorry to hear that the job market is so rough! Reading this brings me back to about three years ago, when I was looking for a job (ANY JOB) for months and months. I joked with my friend (who was also looking at the time) that if we could get $1 for every rejection call/letter we get, we would be so rich! Urgh!', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US) AppleWebKit/532.0 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/3.0.195.33 Safari/532.0', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
