('30811', '406', 'Kirsty Logan', 'hello@kirstylogan.com', 'http://www.kirstylogan.com', '94.195.140.126', '2009-12-23 16:29:27', '2009-12-23 20:29:27', 'Gosh, you don\'t sound at all like I expected! I like the lisp though.\r\n\r\nI will be sad if you don\'t send another story to FW. Writing that email made me realise that when editors say they want to see more of your work, they really actually do.\r\n\r\nI am writing this wearing fingerless gloves and pink fluffy slippers because it\'s cold cold cold in Glasgow. And I consent to that being added to the sexy images list.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.5; en-US; rv:1.9.1.6) Gecko/20091201 Firefox/3.5.6', '', '0', '0', 'Y'),
