('30827', '414', 'LJ', 'ljose@mtu.edu', '', '184.49.148.70', '2009-12-28 00:31:13', '2009-12-28 04:31:13', 'Sad and yet funny (funny only because you are such a talented writer). I\r\nEchoes my experience, although I didn\'t get stuck in a driveway. But there was a fire across the street from my apartment the morning I left. Ice and fire. Perfect oxymoron to describe the emotional rollercoaster these holidays have been for me this year. \r\n\r\nLet\'s make a promise to ourselves: wherever we end up and whatever we do next year, let\'s make sure we will be in a situation where we can go HOME for Christmas and spend the holidays with our families.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.5) Gecko/2008120122 Firefox/3.0.5 (.NET CLR 3.5.30729)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
