('30977', '435', 'W. Lotus', 'wlotus2008@gmail.com', '', '74.72.92.8', '2010-01-15 11:33:15', '2010-01-15 15:33:15', 'I can\'t say much of anything about the tragedy--what an understatement--because it is overwhelming to me even without having loved ones there.\r\n\r\nNo one deserves this.  I recently told my niece, who suffered abuse at the hands of her mother, \"There is nothing in the world you could have done to deserve what she did to you, not even if you had killed someone.\"  I can\'t fathom trying to have a conversation with someone who believes otherwise.\r\n\r\nI am glad to hear your husband is reporting such difficult news well.  :-)', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X 10_4_11; en) AppleWebKit/531.21.8 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0.4 Safari/531.21.10', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
