('31118', '459', 'Amber', 'Anoellesparks@gmail.com', 'http://Www.ambernoellesparks.com', '166.137.139.28', '2010-02-05 09:06:49', '2010-02-05 13:06:49', 'I was actually very indignant that you weren\'t nominated. You are on my best of list. \r\n\r\nAlso, go to your doc, not a derm, first, b/c the most likely cause of your hair loss is hyperthyroidism and you should get tested for it. Some crazy number like one in five women have it, and it makes your hair fall out--and it\'s an easy fix, just a pill a day. I know lots of people who have it. So go get tested! It could be stress, also. Just get it checked out so you feel better. :) PSA done.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; U; CPU iPhone OS 3_1_2 like Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/528.18 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Mobile/7D11 Safari/528.16', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
