('34488', '571', 'K.', 'k_eisler@telus.net', 'http://karyneisler.com', '207.6.241.63', '2010-04-01 12:27:09', '2010-04-01 16:27:09', 'Like Tanya, twice in my life my hair fell out big time. Once as a kid, the other time as an adult. As an adult, I was under great stress, finishing undergrad and going through a break-up. Both times, the same thing worked, and my hair returned, thicker and curlier than ever.  I took \'tissue salts\' - homeopathic little salt tablets.  I must have been really deficient.  I have included a link below. I buy them in natural pharmacies or health food stores. Whole Foods carries them.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.holisticonline.com/remedies/Hair/hair_loss_homeopathic.htm', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-US) AppleWebKit/532.5 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/4.1.249.1045 Safari/532.5', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
