('31382', '506', 'W. Lotus', 'wlotus2008@gmail.com', 'http://lotuslandfineart.com', '74.72.92.8', '2010-03-06 20:15:23', '2010-03-07 00:15:23', 'I\'m surprised that you are thin-skinned; as blunt as your criticisms of others are, I assumed they came from a person who cannot be swayed in the least by the criticisms of others!\r\n\r\nYour desire to put your work out there, yet not be noticed amuses me, only because it is so different from my own desire.  I want to put my work out there, be noticed, and be adored for it.  I have to constantly remind myself to put my work out there (whether office work or artistic work) for the joy of producing work that meets or exceeds my own standards, not with the expectation that others will fall at my feet in worship.  :-)', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X 10_4_11; en) AppleWebKit/531.21.8 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0.4 Safari/531.21.10', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
