('34493', '571', 'Roxane', 'roxane@roxanegay.com', 'http://www.roxanegay.com', '24.247.41.152', '2010-04-01 15:18:33', '2010-04-01 19:18:33', 'Thanks for your comment Tanya. I kind of wonder if a relaxer is what set me down this road but I\'ve been relaxing my hair since I was 5 and it has never been a problem. It\'s not knowing what\'s going on that\'s driving me most crazy.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_8; en-US) AppleWebKit/533.2 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/5.0.342.7 Safari/533.2', '', '34487', '1', 'N'),
