('34497', '571', 'alicia', 'aliciadk@gmail.com', 'http://blog.alicia-kennedy.com', '76.8.72.250', '2010-04-01 15:47:04', '2010-04-01 19:47:04', 'Hi, it\'s Alicia the copy editor! Coming out of the woodwork to commiserate...\r\n\r\nI, too, have been experiencing some extremely traumatic hair thinning. My dermatologist said it\'s telogen effluvium--it\'s resting too soon. It has a bunch of triggers (going on/off the pill, stress, diet, but also thyroid problems). I\'m hoping I\'m at the tail end of mine (it\'s only supposed to last 6 months and I have a shady memory of when it started). I\'ve been using tea tree oil, taking vitamins, and am definitely going to get those salts recommended up there now. *Anything.*\r\n\r\nGood luck/be well.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.8) Gecko/2009032609 Firefox/3.0.8', '', '0', '0', 'Y'),
