('40837', '649', 'Susy', 'christinaland@ymail.com', '', '99.48.67.132', '2010-11-14 20:46:10', '2010-11-15 00:46:10', 'Do you think that maybe you\'ve invested too much in the \"validating\" experience of being published by a magazine you obviously respect?  If you\'re that confident in your story, try to find the publication that suits it, rather than trying to change your story to suit the magazine.  It\'s a bit like changing yourself for a boyfriend, when you were perfectly happy before.  As good as it is, maybe it just isn\'t right for you. Don\'t give up on the daydream, but also don\'t forget that it\'s you providing the service and talent, not the other way around.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.0; WOW64; Trident/4.0; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; Media Center PC 5.0; .NET CLR 3.5.21022; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30618; .NET4.0C)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
