('40755', '1053', 'Jason', 'enricopallazo@yahoo.com', 'http://www.jasonmjones.net', '65.242.114.226', '2010-11-10 14:03:49', '2010-11-10 18:03:49', 'Zombies are among one of the more comforting post-apocalyptic scenarios, since the dead rising and attacking the living isn\'t going to happen. I enjoy post-apocalyptic lit and movies for the most part, though I couldn\'t explain what my odd fascination with the end of the world is. With zombies, unlike an asteroid hitting the Earth or a rapidly spreading disease or nuclear annihilation, you can sit back and enjoy the ride without contemplating it as a reality, and sometimes, I find that to be a lot of fun.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.2.12) Gecko/20101026 Firefox/3.6.12', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
