('46623', '1532', 'Len Kuntz', 'lenk98290@hotmail.com', 'http://lenkuntz.blogspot.com', '72.102.92.44', '2011-05-14 23:49:43', '2011-05-15 03:49:43', '\"sometimes i think the body tells the truths we are unable to speak...\"  that\'s a remarkable line, and also the great first line for a story that shatters..  use it.\r\nroxane--you a super special.  i like you.  a lot.  if i wasn\'t married, i would ask you to go steady with me.  for now, though, i\'ll just say: i want to know you better.  keep doing your thing because you are very good at it.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; Trident/5.0)', '', '0', '0', 'Y'),
