('43472', '1218', 'Sara Crowley', 'saracrowley@btinternet.com', 'http://asalted.blogspot.com/', '109.157.47.155', '2011-01-18 18:19:45', '2011-01-18 22:19:45', 'Oh my fucking god - that Mirena advert! Sheez. Bright, breezy voice \"Don\'t use with certain cancers, may cause PID\'s blah blah blah...\" Fuck this. Wow. I use Mirena for my endometriosis - it stops my period so therefore stops the bleed that spreads to places you can\'t get rid of blood from. It has so many fucking side effects it\'s unbelievable. The side effects make me really ill but not quite as ill as the fucking endo so it\'s a bad, unhappy trade. I take the Mirena, I get to function some of the time, and I pay and pay for it in bad health. To see it advertised as some great birth control is annoying. And the way the guy sits in his lawn chair reading his paper oblivious to his kids whilst the woman gets to thank fuck she doesn’t have to give birth again... just weird. (Haha at \"special sauce!) I\'d never use it for birth control when condoms will do the job and not make you really suffer.\r\n\r\nAnyway - no, you can\'t feel it, and it doesn\'t dislodge. It can be left for years (I picture a rusting evil nail device). Personally I\'m looking forward to menopause so I can be shot it.\r\n\r\nAnd the fat thing. Oh my god the fat thing. I hate these shows because they make people think that\'s how I eat. I am fat but I eat really fucking well. I rarely eat junk food. I can\'t cope with much sugar. I love vegetables. These shows take some excessive eater who exists on cream cakes and chinese take out and 17 bags of crisps and says \"Woah, you could eat so much better than that.\" They put them on a diet and there ya go, they lose weight. Ok, so what about the rest of us fatties. The ones that don\'t eat pies all the day long. I hate my body so much and I so understand you saying \"I am so cute on the inside and I am trying pretty hard to bring that shit in line with my outside self.\" Amen.', '0', '1', 