('44112', '1263', 'robert', 'robert@robertswartwood.com', 'http://www.robertswartwood.com', '70.15.121.157', '2011-02-07 03:37:15', '2011-02-07 07:37:15', 'Yes, the Q&amp;A session for the panel was way too short. I really wish we could have spent at least another hour talking. I think the crowd would have been fine with that. \r\n\r\nGreat to finally meet you, Roxane! It was fun hanging out. And sorry to hear you threw up before the panel. Now I feel bad that I texted you \"Get your butt up here,\" though, in my defense, you had told me to. :-) But you did great. Thanks for helping out on the panel.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_6_6; en-US) AppleWebKit/534.13 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/9.0.597.84 Safari/534.13', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
('44122', '1263', 'Amber', 'anoellesparks@gmail.com', 'http://www.ambernoellesparks.com', '208.118.163.99', '2011-02-07 14:35:34', '2011-02-07 18:35:34', 'All of my friends that I brought to the PANK/Annalemma/ML reading had a fabulous time. And none of them are writers,and none of them had ever been to a reading before, so that\'s saying quite a lot. I agree with your highlights (though I also really liked Sasha Fletcher\'s reading--I\'d add that to the list)--especially Matthias Svalina. When we got to the book fair, Chris made a beeline for the Diagram table so he could buy that book and let me tell you, that is the only book of poetry he has ever purchased in his life. \r\n\r\nAnyway, thanks again for the opportunity to read. It was really fun. I had people telling me all weekend how much they enjoyed it.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.2.2) Gecko/20100316 Firefox/3.6.2 GTB7.1 ( .NET CLR 3.5.30729)', '', '0', '0', 'Y'),
('44120', '1246', 'Casey Hannan', 'knittingkneedle@gmail.com', 'http://www.casey-hannan.com/', '69.76.186.26', '2011-02-07 13:24:18', '2011-02-07 17:24:18', 'Roxane, you are a magician. My submission found acceptance at SmokeLong. If this were an awards ceremony, I would thank you and then shed one tear, two tears, three tears. Then I would wipe the tears away and blow a kiss to the audience with the same hand.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.2.13) Gecko/20101203 Firefox/3.6.13', '', '44098', '0', 'Y'),
('44119', '1263', 'Roxane', 'roxane@roxanegay.com', '', '139.67.132.48', '2011-02-07 13:23:43', '2011-02-07 17:23:43', 'Hi Dawn. Do let me know what you think of the story. You will receive your PANK 5 with Normally Special when it ships. The release date is 3/1. I do hope you are able to join us at AWP 12. It would be a real pleasure to meet you.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.1; Trident/4.0; SLCC2; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; Media Center PC 6.0; InfoPath.2; .NET4.0C; Tablet PC 2.0)', '', '44118', '0', 'N'),
