('44654', '1318', 'LJ', 'ljose@mtu.edu', '', '12.139.184.209', '2011-02-22 21:42:29', '2011-02-23 01:42:29', 'I just checked and I have more than one pork loin in my freezer. I bought a whole pack when I moved.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.6; en-US; rv:1.9.2.13) Gecko/20101203 Firefox/3.6.13', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
('46134', '1428', 'Jen', 'jen.michalski@gmail.com', 'http://jenmichalski.com', '72.81.196.125', '2011-03-30 11:03:24', '2011-03-30 15:03:24', 'I second the congratulations on the Tiptree nod! But the bulk of my congratulations are reserved for the time and energy you devote to nurturing the minds and spirits of today\'s yoots. It seems to be an endless, thankless job most of the time and it takes a special person to do it. I love reading about your trials and tribulations but also the rewards you find in each encounter. Those in society always wants to belittle young adults, but they\'re never willing to put any effort into reaching the very kids they malign. There are very few special people who can do this, and, more importantly, who want do do this. I\'m proud of you.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-US; rv:1.9.2.16) Gecko/20110319 Firefox/3.6.16 (.NET CLR 3.5.30729) SearchToolbar/1.2', '', '0', '0', 'Y'),
