('44798', '1324', 'David-Glen', 'info@davidglensmith.com', 'http://davidglensmith.blogspot.com/', '99.153.184.205', '2011-02-25 16:50:40', '2011-02-25 20:50:40', 'Your closing paragraph hit home. There were ripples of cause and effect. Domino chain reactions. So, at the risk of ranting too long, and the fact I have my own blog to unwind my subconscious on the matter, I\'ll be brief. \r\n\r\nAfter reading your observation regarding the past anonymous friend, I thought, \'why not?\' —typed out my own Google searches on college connections. Result: instant baggage. The face I sought out passed away in November 2010. Left behind a tacky obituary image and misspelled name in the town paper. No heirs. No possessions. Buried in a nondescript small town in Iowa. And he was a year younger than myself. Athletic. Charmer. Academic plus. \r\n\r\nLeaving me without closure. A James Joyce short story in the flesh. Still processing the shock in fact... something will result from the incident, yes. In an odd manner you words opened out a situation for me, all the way over here in Houston. Wow.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.0; WOW64; Trident/4.0; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; Media Center PC 5.0; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; OfficeLiveConnector.1.5; OfficeLivePatch.1.3; .NET4.0C)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
