('45830', '1413', 'Sara H', 'ssink83@gmail.com', 'http://glorifiedloveletters.blogspot.com', '98.127.65.131', '2011-03-16 14:00:39', '2011-03-16 18:00:39', 'I don\'t get all weirded out by massages but hate hate HATE people touching my face. I don\'t even really touch my own face unless it\'s to put make up on, or wash that make up off. \r\n\r\nI appear to be in minority here, but a 2 hour massage would be just fine with me. The way I ache sometimes, I\'d be fine with it happening daily.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-US) AppleWebKit/534.16 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/10.0.648.133 Safari/534.16', '', '0', '0', 'Y'),
('45501', '1399', 'Ashley Ford', 'acford01@gmail.com', 'http://thechicklitz.com', '24.1.79.176', '2011-03-10 20:21:00', '2011-03-11 00:21:00', 'A year and a half ago my boyfriend broke up with me in a very abrupt fashion. When I went to see New Moon in the theater with my chick friends, I gasped when Edward left Bella and said,\r\n\r\n\"Oh my god. I fucking got New Mooned.\"\r\n\r\nOne of the girls turned to me and nodded emphatically.\r\n\r\nI don\'t bruise. Well, I do bruise. I can feel them, but I can\'t see them. Apparently this means I am at a high risk for blood clotting disorders. I just think it makes me some abusive assholes wet dream.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.1; en-US) AppleWebKit/534.13 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/9.0.597.107 Safari/534.13', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
