('43888', '1246', 'Dawn.', 'dawngrrrl@gmail.com', 'http://nouvelliste.tumblr.com', '65.60.229.228', '2011-01-28 23:26:22', '2011-01-29 03:26:22', 'It seems that every writer has their own holy grail. One of mine, funnily enough, is PANK. :)\r\n\r\nI pre-ordered Normally Special during the super-special \"get PANK 5 for free\" time frame. I am beyond geeked. Shamelessly.\r\n\r\n<i>I am at the point in writing my novel now where I don’t want to stop for sleep, for food, for work. I am starting to understand why people go on writer’s retreats. I could use some uninterrupted time. If I had two or three weeks where I could just focus on writing, I’d have a full draft. I’m in the zone. I’m writing the story in my head constantly. I see every part. I know my characters. I am my main character and now it’s a question of getting the words out. Once I get the words out, I’ll know what to do next.</i>\r\n\r\nAnd this is the part I love best.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.1; en-US; rv:1.9.2.13) Gecko/20101203 Firefox/3.6.13', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
