('46514', '1505', 'Babe Runner', 'letitiamoffitt@yahoo.com', 'http://baberunner.blogspot.com/', '139.67.135.212', '2011-05-02 19:36:27', '2011-05-02 23:36:27', 'A huge THANK YOU to you and T and M and the whole team.  Running a marathon is an act of masochistic self-indulgence; cheering on someone running a marathon the way you all did is an act of kindness so great it humbles me right down to my gross smelly running shoes.  I\'d be dead back at mile 8 if not for your support.  And yet I live!  Thank you again.  And again.  And again.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 5.1)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
