('47069', '1673', 'Robert Laughlin', 'pc-privconfounder@sbcglobal.net', '', '71.138.26.136', '2011-07-10 01:02:48', '2011-07-10 05:02:48', 'I did not enter my earlier comment with the intention of ridiculing Roxane. In fact, I was among those who voted for her this year, as I commented in an earlier topic. After she unfortunately became a Million Writers Award bridesmaid the second year in a row, I thought she might appreciate a comedy relief comment from a person who has followed her career and is reasonably familiar to her. (If I recall correctly, she corresponded with me when I was running the Micro Award the third year.) I repeat, no harm was intended to Roxane.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 5.1; Trident/4.0; InfoPath.1; yie8)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
