('47073', '1673', 'Stella', 'casualflocks@gmail.com', '', '98.199.79.101', '2011-07-10 23:00:26', '2011-07-11 03:00:26', 'Roxane, this is such a gorgeous post.  Your writing thrills and nourishes.  \r\n\r\nI agree with you about farm equipment.  My best friend\'s family had a baling machine when I was  a kid, and I loved watching it.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; WOW64; Trident/5.0)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
('47074', '1673', 'Stella', 'casualflocks@gmail.com', '', '98.199.79.101', '2011-07-10 23:12:15', '2011-07-11 03:12:15', 'Forgive me, I only read to the thunderstorm pictures previously -- I was horrified and sad, but not surprised, to read about what you overheard your classmate saying you being there because of \'affirmative action.\'\r\n\r\nYou are so obviously, shiningly, overwhelmingly honest, and brilliant that her motives are clear to me:  she was jealous of you.  Your brilliance drove her crazy.  So she used that to dehumanize you and soothe her pathetic ego.\r\n\r\nI know you know this already.  I\'m just so sorry to think of you running into people like that, because you are splendid.  Anyone with 1/8 of a brain would be celebrating being in the same program with someone as extraordinarly gifted as you.  XOXO', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; WOW64; Trident/5.0)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
('47075', '1673', 'Stella', 'casualflocks@gmail.com', '', '98.199.79.101', '2011-07-10 23:15:46', '2011-07-11 03:15:46', 'And of course, anyone with a whole brain would be overjoyed to have a chance to study alongside someone with your gifts.\r\n\r\nYou don\'t need to admit this, but you\'re so blazingly gifted, I\'m thinking you must know.  It\'s good to know.  Keep that with you, the way you keep your joy in thunderstorms.', '0', '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; WOW64; Trident/5.0)', '', '0', '0', 'N'),
